ZH: 我今天去考场考试。
EN: I am going to the exam hall to take the test today.

ZH: 考场里有很多考生在认真答题。
EN: There are many test takers answering questions seriously in the exam hall.

ZH: 我在考场里遇到了一个老朋友。
EN: I met an old friend in the exam hall.

ZH: 考场的环境很安静。
EN: The exam hall is very quiet.

ZH: 明天考场里将举行一场重要考试。
EN: There will be an important test held in the exam hall tomorrow.

ZH: 考场设备齐全。
EN: The exam hall is well-equipped.

ZH: 考场内不能吃东西。
EN: No eating is allowed in the exam hall.

ZH: 考场外有许多家长在等待孩子考试结束。
EN: There are many parents waiting for their children outside the exam hall.

ZH: 考场内有监考人员监督考试。
EN: Invigilators supervise the test inside the exam hall.

ZH: 考生们都在为考场摩拳擦掌。
EN: Test takers are all ready for the exam in the exam hall.

ZH: 考场的氛围让人心情紧张。
EN: The atmosphere in the exam hall makes people nervous.

ZH: 在考场里，不准互相交流。
EN: No communication is allowed in the exam hall.

ZH: 这个周末我要在考场里参加两个考试。
EN: I will take two tests in the exam hall this weekend.

ZH: 考场是一个公平的竞争场所。
EN: The exam hall is a fair competition place.

ZH: 考场保持安静非常重要。
EN: It is important to keep the exam hall quiet.

ZH: 考场外有服务台可以提供帮助。
EN: There is a service counter outside the exam hall for assistance.

ZH: 考场内的桌子排列整齐。
EN: The tables in the exam hall are neatly arranged.

ZH: 考生们要遵守考场规则。
EN: Test takers must abide by the exam hall rules.

ZH: 考场的监考人员非常严格。
EN: The invigilators in the exam hall are very strict.

ZH: 考场距离我家不远。
EN: The exam hall is not far from my home.
